==English==

===Etymology===
From a {{etyl|cmn|en}} term which means "south of the lake" referring to Lake Dongting.

===Alternative forms===
* Chinese: 湖南
* pinyin: Húnán
* sometimes called 湘 (pinyin: Xiāng) for short, after the Xiang River which runs through the province.

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
{{wikipedia}}

# A province of the [[People's Republic of China]], located in the middle reaches of the Yangtze River and south of Lake Dongting.

